org.codehaus.jackson.map.deser

Class Creator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codehaus.jackson.map.deser.Creator

  • abstract class Creator
extends java.lang.Object
    Container for different kinds of Creators; objects capable of instantiating (and possibly partially or completely initializing) POJOs.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      (package private) static class  Creator.Delegating
      Creator implementation used for cases where parts of deserialization are delegated to another serializer, by first binding to an intermediate object, and then passing that object to the delegate creator (and then deserializer).
      (package private) static class  Creator.NumberBased
      Creator implementation that can handle simple deserialization from Json Number values.
      (package private) static class  Creator.PropertyBased
      Creator implementation used to handle details of using a "non-default" creator (constructor or factory that takes one or more arguments that represent logical bean properties)
      (package private) static class  Creator.StringBased
      Creator implementation that can handle simple deserialization from Json String values.
